title: Um Dia na Vida (Eduardo Coutinho, 2010)
description:
The documentary is a selection of images on network television that Coutinho recorded for 24 hours. It was never released in theaters because of issues related to copyright and image. To this day, Um Dia na Vida (A Day In The Life) could only be shown at film festivals or special meetings attended by the director.
